body_html:
Hi,
I am having the same error using Tensorflow 1.3:
AttributeError: module 'tensorflow.contrib.tfprof' has no attribute 'ProfileContext'

when I use:
with tf.contrib.tfprof.ProfileContext('/tmp/train_dir', trace_steps=[], dump_steps=[]) as pctx:

When I try to import the profiler_context using:
from tensorflow.python.profiler import profile_context

I get: ImportError: cannot import name 'profile_context'

Where can I find the way to import the profiler in Tensorflow 1.3 ?

Thank you!
